text: Jakovljević () is a South Slavic patronymic surname derived from a masculine given name Jakov. It may refer to: *Anto Jakovljević (born 1962), football goalkeeper *Dragan Jakovljević (born 1962), footballer *Robi Jakovljević (born 1993), footballer *Slobodan Jakovljević (born 1989), footballer *Zvonko Jakovljević (born 1996), footballer Category:Croatian-language surnames Category:Serbian-language surnames
title: Jakovljević
